tanstack-form: Guidelines and best practices for using TanStack Form in this project, including usage patterns, component structure, and integration with the custom form system in app/src/components/ui/form.tsx.

# Updated Usage Pattern
- For blur events, always use the internal `field.handleBlur`.
- For change events, always use `(e) => field.handleChange(e.target.value)`.
- For form submission, use:
  ```js
  onSubmit: async ({ value }) => {
    // Do something with form data
    console.log(value);
    // Use value for API calls
  }
  ```
  The `value` object contains all changed form data.
- Integrate with the custom form system in `app/src/components/ui/form.tsx` as needed. 